flowchart TD
    U[User] --> FE[React + Vite SPA]
    FE -->|OAuth / token| FAuth[Firebase Auth]
    FE -->|Bearer token API calls| API[Express API on Cloud Run]

    API -->|verify token + tier| AUTH[Auth Middleware]
    API -->|quota tx + user state| USERS[userService]
    API -->|analysis/readme orchestration| CORE[Service Layer]
    CORE --> GH[GitHub API]
    CORE --> GM[Gemini API]
    CORE --> DB[(Firestore)]

    FE -->|history/results/readmes| API
    FE --> TL[Tally Forms]

    API --> OBS[Logging + Monitoring]
